    slug: "personal-year-numbers",
    excerpt: "Numerology reveals that life moves in nine-year cycles, each year carrying distinct energy and opportunities for growth.",
    content: "Numerology reveals that life moves in nine-year cycles, each year carrying distinct energy and opportunities for growth. Your Personal Year number, calculated from your birth date and the current calendar year, tells you what themes and energies are most active in your life right now.\n\nA Personal Year 1 signals new beginnings and fresh starts. Year 2 brings partnerships and patience. Year 3 is about creativity and self-expression. Year 4 demands hard work and building foundations. Year 5 brings change and adventure. Year 6 focuses on home, family, and responsibility. Year 7 calls for introspection and spiritual growth. Year 8 brings material abundance and power. Year 9 marks completion and release.\n\nUnderstanding your Personal Year number helps you work with the energy of the cycle rather than against it. Trying to start new projects in a Year 9 or seeking solitude in a Year 3 creates unnecessary friction. Alignment with your cycle's energy makes everything flow more naturally.",
