    content: "Crystals absorb, store, and transmit energy, which means they need regular cleansing and charging to function at their best. Just as you would not use a sponge indefinitely without wringing it out, crystals benefit from periodic energetic maintenance.\n\nSeveral cleansing methods are widely practiced. Running water washes away accumulated energy, though not all crystals are water-safe. Selenite plates and singing bowls cleanse through vibrational resonance. Smoke from sage, palo santo, or incense clears stagnant energy. Burying crystals in earth returns them to their source for deep cleansing. Moonlight, especially during a full moon, both cleanses and charges simultaneously.\n\nCharging restores a crystal's energetic potency. Sunlight charges quickly but can fade certain stones. Placing crystals on a large quartz cluster amplifies their energy. Setting clear intentions while holding a crystal programs it for specific purposes. The most important factor in crystal care is consistent attention and respect for these tools.",
