    title: "Biorhythms and Numerology: The Mathematical Cycles Governing Your Energy",
    slug: "biorhythms-and-numerology",
    excerpt: "Biorhythm theory proposes that your physical, emotional, and intellectual capacities follow predictable mathematical cycles from birth.",
    content: "Biorhythm theory proposes that your physical, emotional, and intellectual capacities follow predictable mathematical cycles from the moment of your birth. The physical cycle runs 23 days, the emotional cycle 28 days, and the intellectual cycle 33 days, each following a sinusoidal wave.\n\nWhen a cycle is in its positive phase, that aspect of your being is at peak performance. During the negative phase, rest and caution are advisable. The most interesting moments are the critical days when a cycle crosses zero, which biorhythm proponents associate with increased vulnerability and instability.\n\nCombining biorhythm awareness with numerological cycles creates a layered understanding of personal timing. Your Personal Year number reveals the macro theme, while biorhythms show the micro fluctuations within that larger pattern. Together, they help you make informed decisions about when to push forward and when to rest.",
