    content: "Moldavite is unlike any other crystal. Formed from a meteorite impact in what is now the Czech Republic nearly 15 million years ago, this olive-green tektite carries an energy that many describe as intense, rapid, and deeply transformative.\n\nPeople who work with moldavite often report what has been called the 'moldavite flush': a rush of heat, tingling, or dizziness upon first contact. More significantly, many describe a period of rapid life changes following their first encounter with the stone. Relationships that no longer serve you may end. Career shifts accelerate. Spiritual awakening intensifies.\n\nMoldavite is not for everyone, and it is not a beginner's crystal. Its transformative energy can feel overwhelming if you are not ready for change. Many practitioners recommend pairing moldavite with grounding stones like black tourmaline or smoky quartz to balance its intensity. If you are genuinely ready for transformation, moldavite can be a powerful catalyst.",
