    title: "The Expression Number: What Your Full Name Reveals About Your Purpose",
    slug: "expression-number-full-name",
    excerpt: "Your Expression Number, calculated from the full name given at birth, reveals your natural abilities, talents, and the purpose you are meant to fulfill.",
    content: "Your Expression Number, calculated from the full name given at birth, reveals your natural abilities, talents, and the purpose you are meant to fulfill. While the Life Path shows the road you walk, the Expression Number describes the vehicle you drive on that road.\n\nUsing the Pythagorean chart, convert each letter of your full birth name to its corresponding number, sum them all, and reduce to a single digit (or Master Number). An Expression Number 1 indicates natural leadership. Number 2 suggests diplomatic and intuitive gifts. Number 3 reveals creative and communicative abilities. Number 4 shows organizational strength. Number 5 indicates versatility and adventurousness. Number 6 points to nurturing and teaching abilities. Number 7 reveals analytical and spiritual depth. Number 8 suggests executive capability. Number 9 indicates humanitarian and artistic talents.\n\nUnderstanding your Expression Number can validate gifts you have always possessed but perhaps undervalued. It can also explain why certain roles feel natural while others require exhausting effort despite external success.",
