    slug: "soul-urge-number",
    excerpt: "Your Soul Urge Number, derived from the vowels in your birth name, reveals your innermost desires, motivations, and what truly drives you.",
    content: "Your Soul Urge Number, derived from the vowels in your birth name, reveals your innermost desires, motivations, and what truly drives you at the deepest level. While you may present a certain face to the world, your Soul Urge whispers the truth about what your heart really wants.\n\nTo calculate your Soul Urge, assign Pythagorean values to each vowel (A, E, I, O, U) in your full birth name, sum them, and reduce to a single digit or Master Number. Soul Urge 1 craves independence and achievement. Soul Urge 2 desires partnership and peace. Soul Urge 3 longs for creative expression. Soul Urge 4 seeks stability and order. Soul Urge 5 hungers for freedom and experience. Soul Urge 6 yearns to nurture and be needed. Soul Urge 7 desires truth and spiritual understanding. Soul Urge 8 craves power and material mastery. Soul Urge 9 is driven by compassion and universal love.\n\nWhen your outer life aligns with your Soul Urge, you experience a sense of fulfillment that transcends conventional success. When it conflicts, you may achieve everything society values yet still feel empty.",
