    slug: "personality-number",
    excerpt: "Your Personality Number, calculated from the consonants in your birth name, reveals how others perceive you and the persona you project.",
    content: "Your Personality Number, calculated from the consonants in your birth name, reveals how others perceive you and the persona you project into the world. Think of it as your social filter: the aspects of yourself you allow others to see.\n\nTo find your Personality Number, assign Pythagorean values to each consonant in your full birth name, sum them, and reduce. Personality 1 projects confidence and ambition. Personality 2 appears gentle and cooperative. Personality 3 seems creative and charming. Personality 4 comes across as reliable and disciplined. Personality 5 appears dynamic and adventurous. Personality 6 radiates warmth and responsibility. Personality 7 seems mysterious and intellectual. Personality 8 projects authority and success. Personality 9 appears compassionate and worldly.\n\nThe gap between your Personality Number and your Soul Urge Number often explains the disconnect many people feel between who they appear to be and who they truly are inside. Understanding both numbers helps you bring your outer expression into closer alignment with your inner truth.",
