    slug: "birthday-number-hidden-talents",
    excerpt: "Your Birthday Number, simply the day of the month you were born reduced to a single digit, reveals a special talent that supports your life purpose.",
    content: "Your Birthday Number, simply the day of the month you were born reduced to a single digit or Master Number, reveals a special talent that supports your life purpose. While it carries less weight than your Life Path or Expression numbers, it describes an innate ability that comes naturally to you.\n\nBorn on the 1st, 10th, 19th, or 28th? Your Birthday Number 1 gives you natural leadership and innovation skills. Born on the 2nd, 11th, 20th, or 29th? Number 2 grants intuitive diplomacy. Born on the 3rd, 12th, 21st, or 30th? Number 3 provides creative communication gifts. Each Birthday Number from 1 through 9, plus Master Numbers 11 and 22, describes a specific talent that is uniquely yours.\n\nThink of your Birthday Number as a tool in your pocket. Your Life Path is the journey, your Expression Number is your vehicle, your Soul Urge is the destination your heart desires, and your Birthday Number is a Swiss army knife of natural ability that helps you navigate the road. Understanding it adds nuance to your complete numerological profile.",
